## üé¨ App Preview Video Strategy (iOS)

### Video Structure (15-30 seconds)

**0-3s:** Hook
- "Struggling with task overwhelm?"
- Show frustrated user looking at long to-do list

**3-8s:** Problem
- "Traditional apps don't work for ADHD and autism"
- Show generic productivity app failing

**8-15s:** Solution
- "Meet NeuroNexa - your AI coach that adapts to you"
- Show Nexa breaking down task
- Show breathing exercise
- Show progress celebration

**15-18s:** Social Proof
- "Join thousands finding their focus"
- Show 5-star ratings

**18-20s:** Call to Action
- "Download free today"
- Show app icon and name

### Video Specifications
- Format: MP4 or MOV
- Resolution: 1080p minimum
- Aspect Ratio: 9:16 (portrait)
- Duration: 15-30 seconds
- File Size: <500MB
- Captions: Required (accessibility)

