## ‚≠ê Rating & Review Strategy

### Pre-Launch
- Beta test with 50+ users
- Collect testimonials
- Identify and fix critical bugs
- Ensure 4.5+ star average from beta

### Launch Week
- Prompt satisfied users for reviews (after 3+ days of use)
- Respond to all reviews within 24 hours
- Address negative feedback immediately
- Share positive reviews on social media

### Ongoing
- In-app review prompts after positive interactions:
  - Completing 5 tasks
  - Using app for 7 consecutive days
  - Completing first breathing exercise
- Never prompt after errors or negative experiences
- Respond to reviews professionally and empathetically
- Use feedback to prioritize feature development

### Review Response Templates

**Positive Review:**
```
Thank you so much for your kind words! We're thrilled NeuroNexa is helping you. Your feedback means the world to our team. If you ever have suggestions, we're always listening at support@neuronexa.app üíô
```

**Constructive Feedback:**
```
Thank you for taking the time to share your experience. We hear you on [specific issue] and our team is actively working on improvements. We'd love to learn more - could you email us at support@neuronexa.app? Your input helps us build a better app for everyone.
```

**Bug Report:**
```
We're so sorry you experienced this issue! This isn't the experience we want for you. Our team is investigating immediately. Please email support@neuronexa.app with details so we can help resolve this and make it right. Thank you for your patience.
```

